gram\": \"the tower\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Embedded grooves radiate outwards like rays of light, inspired by a tiara from Chaumet's back catalogue.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chaumet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chaumet\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chaumet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chaumet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Embedded grooves\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"outwards\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"rays\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"a tiara\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as traditional emblems of the Greek goddess Nike and the historic Acropolis in Athens on the reverse side, the organisers have added a small Eiffel Tower, just in case wearers forget where their medals come from.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.7913394617097756, \"rank\": 0.10624935903927418, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1343, \"end\": 1347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"score\": 0.6195614895250893, \"rank\": 0.5537520010283358, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the historic Acropolis\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"Athens\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"the reverse side\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 1406, 